<form method="post" class="login_form">
  title <input type="text" name="post[title]" value="<%= @post.title %>" >
  url <input type="text" name="post[url]" value="<%= @post.url %>" >
  or <br />
  text  <textarea name="post[body]"><%= @post.body %></textarea>
  <button type="submit">submit!</button>
</form>


<p>Leave url blank to submit a question for discussion. If there is no url, the text (if any) will appear at the top of the comments page. If there is a url, the text will be ignored.</p>